    "explanation": "<p>Vitamin $\\mathrm{B}_6$ is also called as pyridoxine.</p>\n<p>Vitamin $\\mathrm{B}_{12}$ is also called as cyanocobalamin.</p>\n<p>Vitamin $B_2$ is also called as Riboflavin.</p>\n<p>Vitamin $B_1$ is also called as Thiamine.</p>",
