    ],
    "correct_options": [
      "B"
    ],
    "answer": null,
    "explanation": "<p>The asparagine amino acid consists of an alpha-amino group ( $-\\mathrm{NH}_2$ ), an alpha carboxylic group $(-\\mathrm{COOH})$ and a side chain of</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mdet3i8x/cfd9a7d2-81b8-470d-acd5-e756c49abbfe/fae28910-6720-11f0-9033-65045f745a44/file-jaoe38c1mdet3i8y.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1mdet3i8x/cfd9a7d2-81b8-470d-acd5-e756c49abbfe/fae28910-6720-11f0-9033-65045f745a44/file-jaoe38c1mdet3i8y.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"TS EAMCET 2023 (Online) 12th May Evening Shift Chemistry - Biomolecules Question 18 English Explanation\"></p>",
