    "explanation": "<p>Fructose possess molecular formula $\\mathrm{C}_6 \\mathrm{H}_{12} \\mathrm{O}_6$. Structure of $D$ and $L$ fructose are</p>\n<p><img alt=\"TS EAMCET 2022 (Online) 20th July Morning Shift Chemistry - Biomolecules Question 2 English Explanation 1\" src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mng61xek/10763a38-35cb-4eb7-9c42-6e6596d18102/981799c0-2dda-11f1-b97b-bd6d58bcbf9a/file-jaoe38c1mng61xel.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1mng61xek/10763a38-35cb-4eb7-9c42-6e6596d18102/981799c0-2dda-11f1-b97b-bd6d58bcbf9a/file-jaoe38c1mng61xel.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<p><img alt=\"TS EAMCET 2022 (Online) 20th July Morning Shift Chemistry - Biomolecules Question 2 English Explanation 2\" src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mng61yru/9f76bfb2-9a4b-4c7e-a204-23a61e426bf3/99264aa0-2dda-11f1-b97b-bd6d58bcbf9a/file-jaoe38c1mng61yrv.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1mng61yru/9f76bfb2-9a4b-4c7e-a204-23a61e426bf3/99264aa0-2dda-11f1-b97b-bd6d58bcbf9a/file-jaoe38c1mng61yrv.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"></p>",
